item.dc:creator: @Play_For_Keeps Play For Keeps
item.description:
@Play_For_Keeps wrote:

I don’t know about that pizza being infinite, but the problem with your account being reset is mostly unexplainable. Usually something to do with your character files.Firstly, just try rebooting your computer and then logging into you character. If that doesn’t work , go into all your server files, and make sure you delete everything that has to do with your account. Then just make a new account. If that doesn’t work, then I have no idea what could be wrong.
